        "content": "<p>When hovering on <code>intros</code> the following infoview appears:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>intros x ...</code> behaves like <code>intro x ...</code>, but then keeps introducing (anonymous) hypotheses until goal is not of function type</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Now, if I try</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">bar</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">intros</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>the state is </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">✝²</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">✝¹</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">✝</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">⊢</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>so <code>lean</code> rightly inserts three anonymous variables. But if I do</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">bar</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">intros</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>the state is </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">⊢</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>exactly as with <code>intro a</code>. <code>lean</code> has not inserted the other two anonymous variables. So I think that the infoview is misleading, because the behaviour of <code>intros</code> and <code>intro</code> is different, while those of <code>intro a</code> and <code>intros a</code> are identical.</p>",
